txt.en: <rgb=#FF0000>Completing 'Restoring the Three Kingdoms' will cancel this quest</rgb>
You have defeated many Jangovar marauders.
You have defeated many Jangovar marauders encroaching on the Dale-lands. Your efforts will ensure the safety of all those within Dale's walls.
'I have heard new reports of Jangovar marauders lurking outside Dale. This cannot stand.\n\n'Meet them in the field, and remind them that they are not welcome in the Dale-lands!'
Jangovar marauders can be found in the wilds near the city of Dale in the Dale-lands.\n\nErna has asked you to defeat any Jangovar marauders you come across.
Jangovar marauders encroach upon the city of Dale and should be dealt with swiftly.
